<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id909022c1-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6" identifier="/us/usc/t22/s5502"><num value="5502">§ 5502.</num><heading> Coordinator for Counterterrorism</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Coordinator for Counterterrorism shall be responsible for the coordination of international aviation security for the Department of State.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id909022c2-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6">(<ref href="/us/pl/101/604/tII/s202">Pub. L. 101–604, title II, § 202</ref>, <date date="1990-11-16">Nov. 16, 1990</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/104/3082">104 Stat. 3082</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
